A directory for some src files used during the development....

opacity: contains an extraction of houdek's code for computing opacities
for use: just tune the path for your ester distrib in opa.f, then make,
then 'opa input param' see example in opa.f

cesam_opa: extraction of cesam2k use of yveline opacities
usage: first 'make a2b' which generates the script converting
opa_yveline.data to opa_yveline.bin (binary)
run the script. then in test_opa.f adapt the PATH the table
opa_yveline.bin and make test_opa and run.
